<plot>A gang of burglars intends breaking into a safety vault under the authority of an over-excited blind man. They did everything to enter... But will they make it out alive!? Please enjoy and look below the surface of what you are seeing to find the satirical meaning of the movie. Our modern society takes care more about the form than the substance. What could happen if we are locked in like in a straight jacket? Helium is a psychiatric comedy at the same time seventies and surrealist with the thriller touch which characterize the aesthetic universe of its filmmaker.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?234729</url></doc>
